- "receiving more than 10 views" means the datasets have been accessed more than 10 times;
- "since the first announcement of their existence" refers to the creation date of a new dataset notification.

sql:
SELECT dataset_id, outlier_method, outlier_value
FROM outlier_detections
WHERE dataset_id = 0 AND outlier_method = 'IQR';

